      "side": 1,
      "message": "why is this needed?\n\nif the intention is to allow calling close multiple times, i am not so sure that\u0027s a great idea. why not change the caller so that it knows what its doing",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 102,
        "startChar": 1,
        "endLine": 102,
        "endChar": 29
      },
      "revId": "7380bf4f7f3abc34611f180db025d5c8f8f67a9d",
