      "writtenOn": "2020-04-01T00:00:57Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "i am worried this will cause occasional panics in L132.\nNormally sending and closing is done by the same piece of code, to guarantee that we don\u0027t attempt to send after closure",
      "revId": "7380bf4f7f3abc34611f180db025d5c8f8f67a9d",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
